cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with automated analysis of cells and tissues via image processing. The use of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) also suggests that it could belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories. Additionally, the paper involves classification of cancer cell lines, which could fall under Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) categories.
